Youssef Fakhr Eddine (Arabic, 15 Jenụwarị 1935 - 27 Disemba 2002) bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri na nwanne nwanyị nke onye na-eme egwuregwu Mariam Fakhr Eiddine.
Nwunye ya Nadia nwụrụ n'ihe mberede ụgbọ ala n'afọ 1974 nke mere ka ọ daa mbà n'obi siri ike, n'ihi ya, ọ hapụrụ ime ihe nkiri wee kwaga biri na Gris ruo ọgwụgwụ ndụ ya.

Ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri iri na isii site n'afọ 1957 ruo 1980 gụnyere ọrụ nkwado na-aga nke ọma dịka ihe nkiri afọ 1967 akpọrọ "Beach of fun" (n'asụsụ Arabic "Chatei el mari") nke Najat Al Saghira gosipụtara.
